  <entry>
    <title>英语每日练1——BlackPink演唱会Jennie中途退场</title>
    <url>/2023/06/28/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E7%BB%831%E2%80%94%E2%80%94BlackPink%E6%BC%94%E5%94%B1%E4%BC%9AJennie%E4%B8%AD%E9%80%94%E9%80%80%E5%9C%BA/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="原文"><a href="#原文" class="headerlink" title="原文"></a>原文</h1><blockquote>
<p>Girl group BlackPink’s Jennie is being slammed online after she was spotted dining at hotpot chain Haidilao in Melbourne on June 11. That was the night Jennie bailed on their sold-out Melbourne arena concert, just five songs into the show. Her  mid-song departure left the remaining members of the quartet , Lisa, Jisoo and Rose to perform the rest of the two-hour concert as a trio. </p>
</blockquote>
<hr>
<h2 id="知识点"><a href="#知识点" class="headerlink" title="知识点"></a>知识点</h2><ol>
<li>slam : 愿意指把门猛地关上，因此也可以表达猛烈抨击某个人</li>
<li>bail out: 愿意指跳伞，这里指的中途离开</li>
<li>five songs into the show: 演唱会唱到第五首歌的时候. (30 minutes into the show )</li>
<li>quertet 四 (trio, duo, solo )</li>
</ol>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>英语每日练</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
  <entry>
    <title>英语每日练2——泰坦号</title>
    <url>/2023/06/30/%E8%8B%B1%E8%AF%AD%E6%AF%8F%E6%97%A5%E7%BB%832%E2%80%94%E2%80%94%E6%B3%B0%E5%9D%A6%E5%8F%B7/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<blockquote>
<p>This morning, an ROV, or Remote Opereted Vehicle from the vessel Horizon Arctic, discovered the tail cone of the Titan submersible , approximately 1600 feet from the bow of  the Titanic on the seafloor. The ROV subsequently found additional debris.</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="知识点"><a href="#知识点" class="headerlink" title="知识点"></a>知识点</h3><ul>
<li>vessel: 船，血管</li>
<li>submersible: 潜水器</li>
<li>tail cone：尾椎</li>
<li>bow： 鞠躬，点头，船首</li>
<li>subsequently：随后</li>
<li>debries: 残骸</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p>In consultation with experts from within the unified command, the debris is consistent with the catastrophic loss of the pressure chamber. Upon this determination, we immediately notified the families. On behalf of the United States Coast Guard, and the entire unified command, I offer my deepest condolences to the families.</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="知识点-1"><a href="#知识点-1" class="headerlink" title="知识点"></a>知识点</h3><ul>
<li>consultation: 商讨</li>
<li>unified command：联合指挥所</li>
<li>be consistent with: 与……一致</li>
<li>notify: 通知</li>
<li>condolence:  吊唁，哀悼，慰问</li>
<li>upon the determination: 经过确认后</li>
<li>chamber: 房间，室，腔，舱</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p>I can only imagine, what this has been like for them. And I hope that discovery provides some solace during the difficult time. Additionally, we’ve been in close contact with the British and French consul general, to ensure that they are fully apprized, and that their concerns are being addressed. the outpouring of support in this highly complex search operation has been robust and immensely appreciated. </p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="知识点-2"><a href="#知识点-2" class="headerlink" title="知识点"></a>知识点</h3><ul>
<li>solace:  安慰，慰藉</li>
<li>consul general： 总领事</li>
<li>apprize： 通知</li>
<li>outpouring： （强烈感情的）倾吐，流露；涌现，喷涌</li>
<li>robust： 强健的，强壮的，强烈的</li>
<li>immensely： 非常</li>
</ul>
<blockquote>
<p>We are grateful for the rapid mobilization of experts on the undersea search and rescue, and we thank all of the agencies and personnel for this full spectrum of international assistance that’s been provided. The ROVs will remain on scene and continue to gather information. Again, our most heartfelt condolences go out to the loved ones of the crew.</p>
</blockquote>
<h3 id="知识点-3"><a href="#知识点-3" class="headerlink" title="知识点"></a>知识点</h3><ul>
<li>mobilization：动员</li>
<li>personnel： 全体人员</li>
<li>spectrum： 范围</li>
<li>crew：全体船员</li>
</ul>
]]></content>
      <tags>
        <tag>英语每日练</tag>
      </tags>
  </entry>
